<p>New to machine learning? Dive into logistic regression in machine learni=
ng with us, a foundational technique in predictive modeling that bridges th=
e gap between simple linear models and complex neural networks in deep lear=
ning. In this article, we will talk about the  logistic regression using Py=
thon, explore its role as a linear model, discuss its application alongside=
 neural networks, and understand how regularization techniques enhance its =
predictive power. Whether you=E2=80=99re a beginner or looking to deepen yo=
ur understanding, join us as we explore the intersection of regression with=
 Python, deep learning, linear models, neural networks, and regularization.=
</p>



